snippet.title: Kingdom Hearts HD 2.5 Remix - Debut Trailer
snippet.description:
The legacy of Kingdom Hearts continues with the next compilation of HD remixed games, including Kingdom Hearts II Final Mix, Kingdom Hearts Birth by Sleep, and HD cinematics for Kingdom Hearts Re:coded.

Kingdom Hearts HD 2.5 Remix will launch exclusively on PS3 in 2014.
